column1: For those of you who are still interested, the Democrats have totally forgotten about DACA. Not a lot of interest on this subject from them!
My daughter, Ivanka, just arrived in South Korea. We cannot have a better, or smarter, person representing our country.
The GREAT Billy Graham is dead. There was nobody like him! He will be missed by Christians and all religions. A very special man.
I have been much tougher on Russia than Obama, just look at the facts. Total Fake News!
“The Faith of Donald Trump,” a book just out by David Brody and Scott Lamb, is a very interesting read. Enjoy!
Obama was President up to, and beyond, the 2016 Election. So why didn’t he do something about Russian meddling?
Have a great, but very reflective, President’s Day!
Melania and I met such incredible people last night in Broward County, Florida. Will never forget them, or the evening!
Cannot believe how BADLY DACA recipients have been treated by the Democrats…totally abandoned! Republicans are still working hard.
Just spoke to Governor Rick Scott. We are working closely with law enforcement on the terrible Florida school shooting.
Jobless claims have dropped to a 45 year low!
I will be meeting with Henry Kissinger at 1:45pm. Will be discussing North Korea, China and the Middle East.
Congratulations to the Philadelphia Eagles on a great Super Bowl victory!
